or newsletter"><input type="submit" class="submitBtn" value=""></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="InnerpageBodyRightPannel">\r\n<div class="InnerpageBodyRightInnerPannel">\r\n<div class="cd-tabs">\r\n	<nav class="InnerpageTabHeder">\r\n		<ul class="cd-tabs-navigation">\r\n			<li><a data-content="Overview" href="#0">overview</a></li>\r\n			<li><a data-content="CMD" class="selected" href="#0">CMD</a></li>\r\n		</ul> <!-- cd-tabs-navigation -->\r\n	</nav>\r\n\r\n<ul class="cd-tabs-content">\r\n<li data-content="Overview" class="selected" style="color:#fff;"><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Genesis</h1><p>The domain of Real Estate nearly three decades ago was notorious for its murky wheeling  dealing practices and short changing of customers. The entry of Narne Estates into this field came like a gust of fresh air. Narne Estates with its penchant for ethical business practices and uncompromisingly rigid stance on principles blew away the cobwebs of mistrust and gave this industry the respectability it was lacking. No wonder it is said that Narne''s ''Redefined Real Estate''.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">The Midas Touch</h1><p>Narne Estates is famous for its Midas Touch. Each venture of Narne Estates has turned out to be a gold mine for its customers. Farsightedness with an uncanny knack of identifying potential prime properties has assured our customers a Win-Win situation  always and every time.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Real Estate with Real Values</h1><p>SMART is what we at Narne Estates believe in. Sincerity, Morality, Accountability, Responsiveness and Transparency are the core values which guide each and every transaction at Narne Estates. So when you think of Real Estate with Real Values, think of Narne Estates.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Jewels in the Narne Estates Crown</h1>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Golden Heights Residency:</span> The Kohinoor of the Real Estate World.</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Grand View Jubilee Hills:</span> Hill top plots for those on the top.\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Central Park:</span> Ecologically charged, Technologically Driven.\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Rolling Meadows:</span> For the tranquil experience.</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">East City:</span> Discover clean air, green trees, even wilderness in the city.</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Jade Gardens:</span> Your Paradise on Earth.</p>\r\n<h1 class="TitleInnerpageW">NARNE GROUP OF COMPANIES</h1><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Narne Publications</h1><p>It is the sole distributor for Andhra Pradesh (except twin cities) of Employment News, one of the most widely circulated employment related weeklies. It is also the sole distributor of the AP Journal as well as for Government of India and Parliamentary Publications.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Narne Aquamarine Estates Ltd.</h1><p>This is a 100% Export Oriented Unit (EOU) with extensive growth ponds for rearing Black Tiger Shrimp and is located at Vutukur Village in Nellore District of Andhra Pradesh.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Narne Constructions Pvt Ltd.</h1><p>As a natural extension of the activities of Narne Estates, this company has been established to undertake all construction work for the jewels in the crown of Narne Estates.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Market Space Systems Pvt Ltd.</h1><p>Marketspace Systems Pvt Ltd., was established in 1999 as the software arm of the Narne Group of Companies as part of our diversification strategy. The company has worked on projects involving technologies for various industry verticals and has successfully implemented projects involving the latest technologies for several top notch organizations. Located in the corporate office premises, this spacious centrally air-conditioned facility has state of the art equipment and has wireless Local Area Networks.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Our Invaluable Asset</h1><p>Our most invaluable asset is our highly dedicated team of staff members for whom the work at Narne''s is not just a job but a mission. It is this missionary zeal which has enabled the Narne Group to grow from strength to strength.</p></li>\r\n\r\n<li data-content="CMD" class="selected" style="color:#fff;">\r\n<div class="InnerSubTabbed">\r\n<span class="TextLinkz"><a href="CMD.html">Chairman Profile</a></span><span class="TextLinkz"><a href="CMDdmessage.html">Chairman Message</a></span><span class="TextLinkz Selecteda">AWARDS</span></div>\r\n<div class="InnerPagerTabbedHeaderFullContent">\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Udyog Ratan Award.</span></p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Manav Seva Puraskar.</span></p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Transworld Goldstar Glory of India - International Award.</span></p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Certificate for Fair Business Practices.</span></p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Certificate of Excellence (for productivity, quality customer service and innovative Management).</span></p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Chief Patron and Founder President of Andhra Pradesh Real Estate Developers Association (APREDA).</span></p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Founder & Governing Council Member of National Real Estate Development Council (NAREDCO).</span></p>\r\n<div class="AwardsWraper">\r\n<div class="AwardPannel"><a href="Awards/Award1b.png" class="lightbox_trigger"><img src="http://localhost/Narnewordpress/wp-content/themes/narne/Awards/Award1s.png"></a></span>\r\n<div class="ZoomIcon"></div></div>\r\n<div class="AwardPannel"><a href="Awards/Award2b.png" class="lightbox_trigger"><img src="http://localhost/Narnewordpress/wp-content/themes/narne/Awards/Award2S.png"></a></span>\r\n<div class="ZoomIcon"></div></div>\r\n<div class="AwardPannel"><a href="Awards/Award3b.png" class="lightbox_trigger"><img src="http://localhost/Narnewordpress/wp-content/themes/narne/Awards/Award3s.png"></a></span>\r\n<div class="ZoomIcon"></div></div>\r\n<div class="AwardPannel"><a href="Awards/Award4b.png" class="lightbox_trigger"><img src="http://localhost/Narnewordpress/wp-content/themes/narne/Awards/Award4s.png"></a></span>\r\n<div class="ZoomIcon"></div></div>\r\n<div class="AwardPannel"><a href="Awards/Award5b.png" class="lightbox_trigger"><img src="http://localhost/Narnewordpress/wp-content/themes/narne/Awards/Award5.png"></a></span>\r\n<div class="ZoomIcon"></div></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n</li>\r\n	</ul> <!-- cd-tabs-content -->\r\n</div></div></div></div></div>\r\n\r\n    </div>', 'Awards', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-10 12:53:21', '2015-07-10 12:53:21', '', 15, 'http://localhost/Narnewordpress/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
