(65, 1, '2015-07-11 09:19:04', '2015-07-11 09:19:04', '[URIS id=60]\r\n<div class="BodyContentWrap">\r\n<p class="BodyWrapP Paragraph">Since its inception, NARNE has been synonymous with a warm place you call home. We believe that the face of Real Estate will be radically different from what it is today, and we work together towards that future. With a deep passion for quality housing, weve built more than 23,000 Residential Flats, and several Commercial Properties in Hyderabad &amp; Bangalore over the last three decades.</p>\r\n<p class="BodyWrapP Paragraph">Our commitment to our customers has been simple: To deliver quality housing at very affordable prices. NARNE essentially means Peoples Favorite. It has lived true to its name, and in the process has been twice declared Most Preferred Builder  South India in a nationwide survey by AC Nielsen.</p>\r\n<p class="BodyWrapP Paragraph">Today, we are keener than ever, to build more, to bring a smile on the faces of people from many more corners of India. Our mission in Real Estate is to achieve more value per square foot in our customers properties: We see ourselves building more than 1,00,000 homes by the year 2016!</p>\r\n<p class="BodyWrapP Paragraph">We at NARNE believe in spreading happiness. We offer affordable Residential Apartments, Duplex Houses, Luxury Flats, Villas and Independent Houses with state-of-the-art amenities within gated communities in Hyderabad &amp; Bangalore.</p>\r\n<p class="BodyWrapP Paragraph BoldFont">For more details, <span class="TitleWrapw">call 040-12 345 6789.</span> Or email us at <span class="TitleWrapw"><a href="file:///F:/Dinanath/NarneUIWork/NarneUI/index.html#">sales@narneestates.com</a></span> Or simply Get Details</p>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'about us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-11 09:19:04', '2015-07-11 09:19:04', '', 4, 'http://localhost/Narnewordpress/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
