us appreciation in the future.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Timely Execution</h1><p>To deliver true benefits, projects must be effectively managed, not only to monitor costs, but also to control scheduling. Our integrated systems, sophisticated infrastructure and professional project management techniques ensure streamlined operations and timely completion.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Transparency</h1><p>Our rock  solid reputation is derived from a strong financial base and an emphasis on completely transparent dealings. A professional information system keeps customers informed of progress at each step of the way. We are also on the approved list of major housing finance companies.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Corporate Philosophy: Customer Service</h1><p>At Narnes, a customer comes first, always and every time. Narnes believes in providing total customer care beginning with selection of plots, advice on investment options,  information of payment schedules and status of accounts to registration of plots and allotment of house loans from reputed financing institutions. Our fully computerized LAN system provides instant, update and accurate information to the customers.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Matchless Infrastructure Development</h1><p>At Narne Estates we believe that customer care means providing complete infrastructure and all modern amenities to enable our customers to lead a stress free quality life. Once you register with Narnes you can rest assured that your investment is safe and property is without encumbrances and with an undisputed title.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Life Long Maintenance:</h1><p>A Narne Customer is a hassle free customer. Once you book a property with Narne Estates, you can forget all your maintenance woes. With a nominal one time collection from each customer, we have set up a corpus fund to look after all your maintenance needs for as long as you are with us.</p>\r\n<h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Advantage  Customer</h1><p>This 