rimp and is located at Vutukur Village in Nellore District of Andhra Pradesh.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Narne Constructions Pvt Ltd.</h1><p>As a natural extension of the activities of Narne Estates, this company has been established to undertake all construction work for the jewels in the crown of Narne Estates.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Market Space Systems Pvt Ltd.</h1><p>Marketspace Systems Pvt Ltd., was established in 1999 as the software arm of the Narne Group of Companies as part of our diversification strategy. The company has worked on projects involving technologies for various industry verticals and has successfully implemented projects involving the latest technologies for several top notch organizations. Located in the corporate office premises, this spacious centrally air-conditioned facility has state of the art equipment and has wireless Local Area Networks.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Our Invaluable Asset</h1><p>Our most invaluable asset is our highly dedicated team of staff members for whom the work at Narne''s is not just a job but a mission. It is this missionary zeal which has enabled the Narne Group to grow from strength to strength.</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul> <!-- cd-tabs-content -->\r\n</div></div></div></div></div>\r\n\r\n    </div>', 'CMD', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-17 07:47:28', '2015-07-17 07:47:28', '', 7, 'http://localhost/Narnewordpress/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
