chnologies for various industry verticals and has successfully implemented projects involving the latest technologies for several top notch organizations. Located in the corporate office premises, this spacious centrally air-conditioned facility has state of the art equipment and has wireless Local Area Networks.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Our Invaluable Asset</h1><p>Our most invaluable asset is our highly dedicated team of staff members for whom the work at Narne''s is not just a job but a mission. It is this missionary zeal which has enabled the Narne Group to grow from strength to strength.</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul> <!-- cd-tabs-content -->\r\n</div></div></div></div></div>\r\n\r\n    </div>', 'CMD', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-24 10:34:18', '2015-07-24 10:34:18', '', 7, 'http://localhost/Narnewordpress/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
