nHeader">AWARDS</span></div></div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="NewsLetterWrapInner"><input type="text" value="subscribe for newsletter"><input type="submit" class="submitBtn" value=""></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="InnerpageBodyRightPannel">\r\n<div class="InnerpageBodyRightInnerPannel">\r\n<div class="cd-tabs">\r\n	<nav class="InnerpageTabHeder">\r\n		<ul class="cd-tabs-navigation">\r\n			<li><a data-content="Overview" href="http://localhost/Narnewordpress/Overview">overview</a></li>\r\n			<li><a data-content="CMD" class="selected" href="http://localhost/Narnewordpress/cmd">CMD</a></li>\r\n		</ul> <!-- cd-tabs-navigation -->\r\n	</nav>\r\n\r\n<ul class="cd-tabs-content">\r\n<li data-content="Overview" class="selected" style="color:#fff;"><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Genesis</h1><p>The domain of Real Estate nearly three decades ago was notorious for its murky wheeling  dealing practices and short changing of customers. The entry of Narne Estates into this field came like a gust of fresh air. Narne Estates with its penchant for ethical business practices and uncompromisingly rigid stance on principles blew away the cobwebs of mistrust and gave this industry the respectability it was lacking. No wonder it is said that Narne''s ''Redefined Real Estate''.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">The Midas Touch</h1><p>Narne Estates is famous for its Midas Touch. Each venture of Narne Estates has turned out to be a gold mine for its customers. Farsightedness with an uncanny knack of identifying potential prime properties has assured our customers a Win-Win situation  always and every time.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Real Estate with Real Values</h1><p>SMART is what we at Narne Estates believe in. Sincerity, Morality, Accountability, Responsiveness and Transparency are the core values which guide each and every transaction at Narne Estates. So when you think of Real Estate with Real Values, think of Narne Estates.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Jewels in the Narne Estates Crown</h