also available with 3 or 4 bedrooms. </p>	\r\n<p class="ProjectTitle TitleMargin">- Design features </p>\r\n<p class="ProjectPtext">Environmentally conscious design with  Geo Biological compatibility, Water Treatment plants, Scenic parks, Medical Centers, Street lighting, Cement concrete roads, Earmarked tot-lots, fully landscaped open areas and amenities like club, school, shopping complexes thus converting  all your dreams to reality. </p>	\r\n<p class="ProjectTitle TitleMargin">- World class specifications </p>\r\n<p class="ProjectPtext">Spread over 40 well planned acres, with wide access cement concrete roads and underground cabling, all units are designed with international space considerations. So for you to live peacefully, all homes are designed as per Vaastu and Fengshui, with consultation made available for an individual, to select suitable units as per year of birth and other parameters. </p>	\r\n<p class="ProjectTitle TitleMargin">- Bare or furnished </p>\r\n<p class="ProjectPtext">All units are available bare or with imported designed furniture, carefully crafted for your home. Choose from the various payment options available, among which finance schemes are also available from leading banks.</p>	\r\n<p class="ProjectTitle TitleMargin">- Our Architect </p>\r\n<p class="ProjectPtext">Golden Heights Residency is designed by Hiren Patel and Architects, Ahmedbad. A renowned architect who designed the house of Shri L K Advani, Deputy Prime  Minister of India, his work has been published in many magazines and has won many awards.</p>	\r\n</div>\r\n            </section>\r\n	        </div>\r\n			</div>\r\n            <div class="featuresDiv">\r\n            <div id="demo1" class="ScrollBarWrap">\r\n		<section id="examples">\r\n			\r\n			<!-- content -->\r\n			<div class="content mCustomScrollbar">\r\n<p class="ProjectTitle TitleMargin">- Features</p>\r\n<p class="ProjectPtext">\r\n<div class="scrollListpage">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Three Lakh litres capacity overhead