>   </div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class="InnerPageLeftSubLinksftr">\r\n<div class="InnerPageSocial">\r\n<span class="PlanHeader">AWARDS</span></div></div></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="NewsLetterWrapInner"><input type="text" value="subscribe for newsletter"><input type="submit" class="submitBtn" value=""></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="InnerpageBodyRightPannel">\r\n<div class="InnerpageBodyRightInnerPannel">\r\n<div class="cd-tabs">\r\n<div class="servicesWrapz">Services</div>\r\n\r\n<ul class="cd-tabs-content">\r\n<li data-content="Overview" class="selected" style="color:#fff;"><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Introduction</h1><p>Narne Estates is the leading real estate developer in Andhra Pradesh with a track record of having developed nearly 5000 acres in the twin cities in a span of over two decades. Narne Estates believes in the <span class="hightText">SMART</span> way of operating where Sincerity. <span class="hightText">M</span>orality, <span class="hightText">A</span>countability, <span class="hightText">R</span>esponsiveness, and Transparency are the core values which guide each and every transaction at Narne Estates. No wonder the Narne family comprises of over 20,000 fully satisfied customers.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Real Estates Solutions:</h1><p>We realize that several factors go into providing real estate solutions that protect customer investment  most importantly, Location, Design, Quality, Cost-Effectiveness, Timely Execution, Transparency and Customer Service. These are the fundamentals of our approach.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Location:</h1><p>One way of identifying the best areas in the twin cities is to look for a Narne Properties Project. Our policy of building up reserves of prime land ensures that our projects offer the best address.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Design</h1><p>We work with the best architects and our Golden Heights Residency (GHR) Project is characterized by design that is both creative and functional. At the outset, we are focused on the customers who will ultimately inhabit and use the space, and all elements of design concentrate on ensuring that their needs are fulfilled.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Quality</h1><p>From selecting a site to delivering a finished project, quality consciousness pervades all our operations. It is our firm belief that not only do quality projects constantly increase in value, they are also easier to maintain in the long run, thus benefiting all those associated with them.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Cost  Effectiveness</h1><p>To understand what makes a project feasible requires experience and long term vision. We study and identify market trends and customer requirements before we embark on construction, and monitor costs at each step of the way. It is our endeavor to always provide options that provide best value  for  money today, and continuous appreciation in the future.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Timely Execution</h1><p>To deliver true benefits, projects must be effectively managed, not only to monitor costs, but also to control scheduling. Our integrated systems, sophisticated infrastructure and professional project management techniques ensure streamlined operations and timely completion.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Transparency</h1><p>Our rock  solid reputation is derived from a strong financial base and an emphasis on completely transparent dealings. A professional information system keeps customers informed of progress at each step of the way. We are also on the approved list of major housing finance companies.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Corporate Philosophy: Customer Service</h1><p>At Narnes, a customer comes first, always and every time. Narnes believes in providing total customer care beginning with selection of plots, advice on investment options,  information of payment schedules and status of accounts to registration of plots and allotment of house loans from reputed financing institutions. Our fully computerized LAN system provides instant, update and accurate information to the customers.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Matchless Infrastructure Development</h1><p>At Narne Estates we believe that customer care means providing complete infrastructure and all modern amenities to enable our customers to lead a stress free quality life. Once you register with Narnes you can rest assured that your investment is safe and property is without encumbrances and with an undisputed title.</p><h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Life Long Maintenance:</h1><p>A Narne Customer is a hassle free customer. Once you book a property with Narne Estates, you can forget all your maintenance woes. With a nominal one time collection from each customer, we have set up a corpus fund to look after all your maintenance needs for as long as you are with us.</p>\r\n<h1 class="TitleInnerpage">Advantage  Customer</h1><p>This is achieved by adhering to our full proof time tested <span class="hightText">C-7 formula,</span> whose ingredients are:</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Compact :</span> At single point.</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Capability :</span> Sound support infrastructure\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Competence :</span> Professional Setup.\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Consistency ;</span> Quality Assurance.</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Credibility :</span> Impeccable track Record.</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Cost Effectiveness :</span> Value for Money.</p>\r\n<p class="listStyleHeading" style="margin-bottom:17px;"><span class="HeadingTitle">Confidence :</span> Ability to Deliver.</p></li>\r\n<!-- cd-tabs-content -->\r\n</div></div></div></div></div>\r\n\r\n    </di